{"tid":2173436,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女社工涉阻差 督察：騷證要求不合理","createTime":"2020-08-25T08:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T09:55:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"93035097fad72333fab0efa40c3622a4460c54b7","tid":2173436,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:37:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/XU4JLH5IYNFTXFTFS6RGKU52MY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FXU4JLH5IYNFTXFTFS6RGKU52MY%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXc04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=08336632\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FXU4JLH5IYNFTXFTFS6RGKU52MY%2F&h=a855ad58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/XU4JLH5IYNFTXFTFS6RGKU52MY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n女社工涉阻差 督察：騷證要求不合理<br />\n<br />\n■社工林曉樺涉因拒絕出示身份證而被控阻差辦公。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8月25日網民發起荃葵青遊行，最後爆發警民衝突，同晚有女社工在荃灣被指拒絕出示身份證，並要求女督察展示委任證，最終被控阻差辦公罪。案件昨開審，防暴女督察稱截查被告時，被告看到她與同袍都穿警察制服，認為對方仍要求她出示委任證的要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n報稱任社工。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n事發時隸屬港島衝鋒隊第四小隊指揮官的女督察梁敏儀供稱，她與同袍穿上防暴裝，事發當晚巡至荃灣街市街及眾安街，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方指被告有出示身份證<br />\n<br />\n辯方引述《警察通例》稱，除非情況不容許或要求不合理，否則市民若提出要求，軍裝警應出示身份證。梁答被告有權這樣做，但認為被告的要求影響警方行動，亦不合理，因她與同袍都穿上制服。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指梁所穿的背心有位置放委任證，但看不到她和其他警員有顯示委任證。辯方問梁是否「故意唔擺」，梁答「冇咁嘅規定要我哋擺」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方認為梁其實是因遭被告阻礙工作，為報復才拘捕被告，而被告亦有出示身份證。梁否認，並強調被告被捕後才出示身份證。<br />\n<br />\n男警李俊傑則指，因見到同袍執行指令有困難，出於息事寧人而上前展示委任證，但他很快轉頭，沒為意被告有否出示身份證。裁判官裁定兩罪表證成立，案件今續審<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3485/19<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_GjCOqeELBZlRGOIBrbR1diN_7I=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/24NW2MBWJJA33GXGUDPN4F37LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_GjCOqeELBZlRGOIBrbR1diN_7I%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F24NW2MBWJJA33GXGUDPN4F37LY.jpg&h=219d4a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女督察梁敏儀認為被告要求她出示委任證不合理。"},{"pid":"5527e5909a86a9a4f7acc5de5a9700297d88ce46","tid":2173436,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都夠膽傳上庭"},{"pid":"cff86e3a67892f8ed0a18c19e28de2bd3ae93adf","tid":2173436,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:38:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0201cb3918b67b6351631fb2b976f10f88da9871","tid":2173436,"uid":49258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:38:43.000Z","msg":"女督察<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f460d491f7bd8726cdf98e275304960c5886f124","tid":2173436,"uid":156579,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:40:09.000Z","msg":"反而show完張證我會覺得係假證<br />\n性別果度錯嫁wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba193b3795fe74be8a1088f6efa45cfe60719518","tid":2173436,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ukRuWJa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FukRuWJa.png&h=fcd58abc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47686499134957c93c6b48c1ea5f0741c97c0e92","tid":2173436,"uid":46669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:40:38.000Z","msg":"切左jerjer就係女人呀？"},{"pi